rComments: Great professor and very caring. Sticks to the syllabus which I think is the reason why some students complained. Very accessible outside course hours to answer questions and provide clarifications. Cares about her students.

One of the best professors I had so far. I decided to take the course with her because my brother took a course with her previously and was impressed by her approach. She really cares, provides feedback, and answers questions throurougly and quickly. I wish I was able to attend her classes in person.

You can pass the class with good amount of reading the lecture and the book. However be very careful of the final exam it is thought no to say the least compare to her quizzes and example and it is worth 50%.
